#  **Module 9: Docker Compose (Multi-Container Systems)**

### Objective

Run real applications (not single containers)

### Topics

* docker-compose basics
* YAML structure
* Services
* Volumes and networks in compose
* Environment variables

### Lab

* Build app + database setup
* Run multi-container system
* Scale services

